trans-unit.source: Specifies the function of an item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Angir funksjonen av et element i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The ListViewItemType enumeration identifies the function of items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen ListViewItemType identifiserer funksjonen av elementer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>

trans-unit.source: You can use the ListViewItemType enumeration to identify the type of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke ListViewItemType opplistingen til å identifisere en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem>

trans-unit.source: A data item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control.
An empty item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Et tomt element i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The empty item is displayed when the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control has no records to display, or when a group in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control has no more records to display.
trans-unit.target: Tomt element vises når den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"> </xref> kontrollen har ingen oppføringer å vise, eller når en gruppe i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"> </xref> kontrollen har ingen flere poster for visning.

trans-unit.source: An insert item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control.
